Package: tagger
Type: Package
Title: Survey Question Tagging and JSON-LD Utilities
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Tagger", family = "Maintainers", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "maintainers@example.com")
Description: Tools to import survey data, build hierarchical clusters of question text,
    assign hierarchical tags with Ollama, and export survey entities as JSON-LD.
